{"tid":1761973,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華為官方Twitter粗口鬧蘋果    華為：賬號被盜用 已刪文","createTime":"2019-11-29T09:00:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-01T06:34:49.000Z","uid":184679,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c261f96a1e88f4f96ea663a23e83ba3f7c5c7bf8","tid":1761973,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T09:00:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/fin/20191129/s00010/1fca1697ab2ac0a2239078d868bf0bf6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2F20191129%2Fs00010%2F1fca1697ab2ac0a2239078d868bf0bf6.jpg&h=405dc37e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n華為巴西官方Twitter出現粗口攻擊蘋果公司的內容。華為回應指，因官方賬號被盜用，強調帖文並非由工作人員發布，員工發現後已立即刪除該帖文。<br />\n<br />\n華為又指，集團巴西Twitter官方賬號發布的內容多使用葡萄牙語，惟該攻擊性帖文卻為英語。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1575017153034&amp;issue=20191129\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1575017153034%26issue%3D20191129&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLWLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=e1461060\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1575017153034&amp;issue=20191129</a>"},{"pid":"afcc1782f0b1c01160adeb2151a1c1305212ad0c","tid":1761973,"uid":112416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T09:01:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0a5bfc4cc3853af9965c2ca0d137637aa908dbc","tid":1761973,"uid":229886,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T09:02:26.000Z","msg":"sent by iPhone 11 pro"},{"pid":"3723a08d0c02da6256247bc5899e448e7cb11e9b","tid":1761973,"uid":165159,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T09:03:47.000Z","msg":"官方帳號都俾人 heck <br />\n咁用戶手機咪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f03f4472133477c3ad491265d7bfaff7da1bb1ee","tid":1761973,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,